text:
Practical  Assessment  –  AI  Prototyping  
Engineer
 
TASK  1:  LLM-Powered  AI  Prototype  (Mandatory)  
Build  one  working  prototype:  
●  Chat  with  PDFs  ●  Resume  screening  assistant  ●  Internal  knowledge  bot  ●  AI  form  auto-filler  
Requirements  
●  LLM  (OpenAI  or  open-source)  ●  RAG  (embeddings  +  vector  DB)  ●  Chunking  strategy  ●  Prompt  engineering  ●  Basic  UI  (Streamlit  /  FastAPI)  
Must  explain  design  choices.  
TASK  2:  Hallucination  &  Quality  Control  
Problem  
      LLM  gives  confident  but  incorrect  answers.  
What  to  Deliver  
●  Causes  of  hallucination  in  your  system  ●  At  least  2  guardrails  implemented  ●  Examples  of  improved  responses  
Examples:  
●  Confidence  thresholds  ●  Source-grounded  answers  ●  Prompt  constraints

TASK  3:  Rapid  Iteration  Challenge  
Goal  
Add  one  advanced  capability :  
●  Feedback  loop  ●  Memory  ●  Cost  optimization  ●  Multi-document  reasoning  ●  Tool  calling  
Explain:  
●  Why  you  chose  it  ●  Trade-offs  ●  Limitations  
TASK  4:  AI  System  Architecture  
Problem  
Design  an  AI  assistant  for  enterprise  internal  use .  
Must  include:  
●  Data  ingestion  ●  Vector  DB  choice  ●  LLM  orchestration  ●  Cost  control  ●  Monitoring  &  evaluation  
 
Diagram  +  explanation.  
AI  Prototyping  Engineer  Submission  
●  GitHub  repo  ●  Live  demo  (optional)  ●  README  explaining  architecture  &  trade-offs.
